FuncDef:
The transceiver non-certified-alarm disable command disables the alarm function for non-Huawei-certified optical modules.
The undo transceiver non-certified-alarm disable command enables the alarm function for non-Huawei-certified optical modules. The transceiver non-certified-alarm disable command disables the alarm function for non-Huawei-certified optical modules. The undo transceiver non-certified-alarm disable command enables the alarm function for non-Huawei-certified optical modules. By default, the alarm function is enabled for non-Huawei-certified optical modules.
